Producer Juliet explained to us what the definition of "the ick" is, and we wanted to see
                if we gave our wives the ick in any way. Ben described his VERY ENJOYABLE shopping after a few beers,
                and we think we've been culled from our friend's baby...

Mondeeeeeee how are ya! Our country has really expanded its vocabulary since Covid hit;
                Cluster... community transmission... outbreak... the list goes on! So Ben called a cafe and tried to
                book a table, but the challenge was he had to drop as many of...
